Name: teratocarcinoma
Definition: A mixed germ cell tumor that is a mixture of teratoma with embryonal carcinoma

Name: teratoma
Definition: A germ cell and embryonal cancer that is an encapsulated tumor with tissue or organ components resembling normal derivatives of all three germ layers.

Name: trophoblastic neoplasm
Definition: A germ cell and embryonal cancer that derives_from trophoblastic tissue.
